# Qubic USA Ambassador Hackathon â€” â€œRevolutionsâ€

The **Qubic USA Ambassador Hackathon â€” Revolutions** is the flagship developer initiative of the Qubic USA Ambassador Program. Its mission is to grow the **RPC-20 ecosystem**, drive **real-world adoption**, and onboard the next generation of **gaming developers, system engineers, and decentralized compute architects**.

At the center of Revolutions is a single challenge:

> **Build the Ultimate Qubic Wallet** â€” a high-performance, Web3-native wallet that combines gaming-grade UX, on-chain asset management, and Qubicâ€™s distributed compute model into one production-ready application.

This wallet is envisioned as the primary entry point for **users, miners, traders, and game studios** to interact with:

- RPC-20 tokens  
- Decentralized games and tournaments  
- Staking mechanisms and yield strategies  
- AI-powered smart contracts and oracles  

---

## Core Vision

For game studios and independent builders, Qubic offers a rare combination in Web3:

- **Feeless micro-transactions**  
  - Ideal for real-time games, wagers, in-game items, and tournaments.

- **On-chain randomness & compute**  
  - Enables provably fair mechanics for poker, arcade games, PvP, and betting.

- **True asset ownership via RPC-20**  
  - Tokens, skins, game passes, IPO shares, and reward pools live on-chain.

- **Distributed AI & game logic**  
  - NPC behavior, matchmaking, fraud detection, and dynamic in-game economies.

The hackathon creates direct pathways for:

- Launching **Qubic-native games**  
- Integrating **paQman, snaQe/snaQle**, and future arcade titles featuring CFB  
- Creating **tokenized tournaments, staking pools, and esports economies**  
- Monetizing through **burn mechanics, IPO shares, and automated reward distribution**

